      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds like a good start. lets dive into the \"dress codes\" part first. if someone wants to look universally professional and high-class, what are the core standards they should follow? like, if they are attending a high-end business gala or a formal dinner, what is the baseline for looking \"sophisticated\"?",
